        <Parent_String>gum resin [300012940], gum resin and gum resin by product [300263584], resin (organic material) [300012882], organic material [300011792], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
